30
00:04:21,820 --> 00:04:24,570
She's quite resourceful at getting information.

31
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,740
Then I'll deal with her once and for all.

32
00:04:32,750 --> 00:04:34,350
Mr. Qiao, where are you going?

33
00:04:34,350 --> 00:04:35,750
To the cocktail reception.

34
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:38,150
- All right. This way, please.
- Thank you.

35
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:43,800
I'm sorry. I originally wanted to let you have this invitation.

36
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:46,200
But in light of the fact that you lose it every time you drink,

37
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:48,150
I came on your behalf.

38
00:04:48,150 --> 00:04:51,600
If you really wanted to be nice, then give me the opportunity to take the training course.

39
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:54,300
After all, I have given in to you enough growing up.

40
00:04:54,300 --> 00:04:56,700
If I let you have it, wouldn't that be pitying you?

41
00:04:56,700 --> 00:04:58,900
You really should be.

42
00:04:58,900 --> 00:05:03,600
You're the kind of person that digs up people's privacy without feeling ashamed. All for page views.

43
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:06,000
You really shouldn't be so stubborn.

44
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:08,700
The opportunity to meet Mr. Qiao today is mine.

45
00:05:08,700 --> 00:05:10,685
Hurry on back.

46
00:05:11,423 --> 00:05:12,823
You!

47
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:15,920
You came.

48
00:05:17,290 --> 00:05:18,370
Yunduan?

49
00:05:18,370 --> 00:05:20,550
I thought you said that you weren't coming.

50
00:05:20,550 --> 00:05:22,370
Su Nian said that she was coming.

51
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:31,220
Can my fiancée come in with me?

52
00:05:31,220 --> 00:05:33,110
Yes, please.

53
00:05:33,110 --> 00:05:34,500
Let's go.

54
00:05:48,860 --> 00:05:51,720
Nian Nian. Nian Nian!

55
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,960
This is your Mojito.

56
00:05:52,960 --> 00:05:55,040
- Thank you.
- Alcohol-free.

57
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,718
You two are getting married tomorrow.

58
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:01,420
But weren't you just friends?

59
00:06:01,420 --> 00:06:04,870
The difference between a friend and a boyfriend is just one word.

60
00:06:07,210 --> 00:06:08,710
Nian Nian.

61
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,050
Nian Nian?

62
00:06:11,050 --> 00:06:14,140
Stop worrying. I'll go get you some food.

63
00:06:19,050 --> 00:06:20,750
Editor Su, Mr. Qiao has arrived at the cocktail reception.

64
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:22,710
You can do the interview directly.

65
00:06:30,220 --> 00:06:32,000
Stop searching! Stop searching!

66
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:35,240
